Find all nearby friends from user current location

GeoSpatial Data
  Dynamic
    Online
    Offline 
    Moving

  Real Time Update

A Person will have many friends online at a time, so both of them should know about each other.

Communication 
  Peer-Peer
  Via Common Server
    2 Way for Real time update
      WebSocket

Event Update
  Whenever anyone location is changed, update all its friends
  Pub/Sub
    Pub when user changes every 30sec
    Sub get notified when friends location is updated
    Redis
      Create a dedicated channel for each user 

