Numbers
  Users 100M
  Friends 400
  Concurrent User 10%
  Location update once in 30sec

  User updatin its location(QPS)(Pub) : 100M * 10% / 30 = 334K
      
  User update to be sent(Sub) = 334K * 400 * 10% = 14 M
